{
  "design_notes": "Designed for Easy difficulty: strictly on-beat or 0.5-beat spacing to prevent complex timing. No crossovers, and holds are strictly matched to the song's key synth sustains, comprising roughly 19% of the total notes. S0 maps a very light, basic intro pattern. S1 increases energy with the first drop, incorporating gentle downbeat jumps (via accented jump density) and easy holds. S2 and S3 provide a clean breather before the massive S4 drop. S4 features our main climax with full drop density, following the song's energy curve. Outro tap wraps up cleanly.",
